                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>Globally, research consistently finds that long screen time especially before bedtime delays sleep, reduces sleep quality, and increases daytime sleepiness. Work-related factors, like long or irregular hours, also contribute to poor sleep and low energy.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
