                  <formatted-text>
                    <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Segoe UI' fontsize='11'>Problem Context</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Segoe UI' fontsize='11'>: </run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>In Bhutan, people living in urban areas often spend more time in front of screens, work longer hours, and move less, which can harm their sleep. On the other hand, rural residents usually follow traditional daily routines, stay active, and go to bed earlier, which may help them sleep better. </run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>Despite these patterns,there is a lack of evidence on how bedtime routines, screen time, and work habits impact sleep quality and daily energy among urban and rural residents in Bhutan. This study aims to compare these lifestyle patterns and their effects on sleep health and wellbeing.</run>
                    <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                    <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>Aim:</run>
                    <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'> The project examines rural–urban lifestyle differences in Bhutan. It compares Bhutanese lifestyles by focusing on average work hours, screen use before sleep, and sleep patterns, and how these factors influence sleep quality and daytime energy levels.</run>
