    <dashboard enable-sort-zone-taborder='true' name='Habits &amp; Support (2)'>
      <style />
      <size maxheight='860' maxwidth='650' minheight='560' minwidth='420' />
      <zones>
        <zone h='100000' id='4' type-v2='layout-basic' w='100000' x='0' y='0'>
          <zone h='97142' id='40' param='horz' type-v2='layout-flow' w='97538' x='1231' y='1429'>
            <zone h='97142' id='19' param='horz' type-v2='layout-flow' w='72923' x='1231' y='1429'>
              <zone h='97142' id='5' type-v2='layout-basic' w='72923' x='1231' y='1429' />
            </zone>
            <zone fixed-size='160' h='97142' id='39' is-fixed='true' param='vert' type-v2='layout-flow' w='24615' x='74154' y='1429' />
          </zone>
          <zone-style>
            <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
            <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
            <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
            <format attr='margin' value='8' />
          </zone-style>
        </zone>
        <zone h='39821' id='10' name='Features ' w='30769' x='25846' y='3929' />
        <zone h='37143' id='13' leg-item-layout='vert' leg-item-order='normal' name='Features ' pane-specification-id='0' param='[federated.052b2qe1aire4u15i32y411tifre].[none:Calculation_1344475699896322:nk]' type-v2='color' w='21385' x='2000' y='1607' />
        <zone h='36607' id='32' name='Adoption potential ' w='35538' x='1692' y='45357' />
        <zone h='15357' id='34' name='Adoption potential ' pane-specification-id='0' param='[federated.052b2qe1aire4u15i32y411tifre].[none:willing_to_try_app_code:ok]' type-v2='color' w='17692' x='40923' y='56429' />
        <zone forceUpdate='true' h='81250' id='41' type-v2='text' w='38000' x='61231' y='1786'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>The chart shows that the most preferred feature in a sleep support mobile app is reminders to reduce screen use (21.68%), indicating that users value help in limiting phone usage before bedtime. </run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>Other popular features include sleep tracking statistics (15.40%), tips for better bedtime (14.59%), and tools to help manage schedules (14.18%), suggesting that users are interested in both guidance and monitoring of their sleep habits.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>Features like education (14.08%) and relaxation or breathing exercises (13.17%) are also moderately preferred. SMS reminders (6.89%) are the least preferred, showing lower interest in this type of notification.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone h='16786' id='42' type-v2='text' w='96000' x='2923' y='83214'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>In terms of willingness to use such an app, a majority of respondents (58.42%) said they would be willing to try it, while 36.65% are unsure and only 4.93% are not willing. This indicates a strong potential interest in a sleep-support app, especially if it includes useful and relevant features.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
      </zones>
      <devicelayouts>
