    <dashboard enable-sort-zone-taborder='true' name='Improvement'>
      <style />
      <size maxheight='860' maxwidth='650' minheight='560' minwidth='420' />
      <zones>
        <zone h='100000' id='4' type-v2='layout-basic' w='100000' x='0' y='0'>
          <zone h='97142' id='19' param='horz' type-v2='layout-flow' w='97538' x='1231' y='1429'>
            <zone h='97142' id='5' type-v2='layout-basic' w='97538' x='1231' y='1429' />
          </zone>
          <zone-style>
            <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
            <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
            <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
            <format attr='margin' value='8' />
          </zone-style>
        </zone>
        <zone h='45536' id='3' name='Habits' w='54154' x='40615' y='3214' />
        <zone h='32321' id='9' name='Habits' pane-specification-id='0' param='[federated.1if0aae0abfevu1em80v90jk2l2x].[none:Calculation_1508853040193536:nk]' type-v2='color' w='26308' x='1692' y='1607' />
        <zone forceUpdate='true' h='41607' id='39' type-v2='text' w='86308' x='7077' y='55536'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>The chart shows that the most common habit believed to improve sleep quality is reducing screen use (20.69%), suggesting that many people think using phones less before bedtime helps them rest better. This is followed by having a stress-free environment (18.14%) and maintaining a consistent sleep time (16.92%), indicating the importance of a calm setting and routine. Relaxing activities (15.09%) are also commonly practiced. In comparison, fewer people selected habits such as exercising regularly (10.50%), avoiding caffeine late (9.68%), and using alarms or reminders (8.97%). </run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>Overall, habits related to reducing stimulation and maintaining routine appear to be more commonly valued for better sleep.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
      </zones>
      <devicelayouts>
        <devicelayout auto-generated='true' name='Phone'>
