      <size maxheight='964' maxwidth='1016' minheight='964' minwidth='1016' />
      <zones>
        <zone h='100000' id='2' type-v2='layout-basic' w='100000' x='0' y='0'>
          <zone h='98340' id='1' param='vert' removable='false' type-v2='layout-flow' w='98426' x='787' y='830'>
            <zone h='3423' id='3' type-v2='title' w='98426' x='787' y='830' />
            <zone fixed-size='149' h='15456' id='4' is-fixed='true' paired-zone-id='5' removable='false' type-v2='flipboard-nav' w='98426' x='787' y='4253' />
            <zone h='79461' id='5' paired-zone-id='4' removable='false' type-v2='flipboard' w='98426' x='787' y='19709'>
              <flipboard active-id='31' nav-type='caption' show-nav-arrows='true'>
                <story-points>
                  <story-point caption='Cover Page' captured-sheet='Dashboard 6' id='18' />
                  <story-point caption='Evidence of Lifestyle Impacts on Sleep and Wellbeing' captured-sheet='Dashboard 15' id='30'>
                    <capturedDeltas>
                      <dashboard name='Dashboard 15'>
                        <zone id='3'>
                          <formatted-text>
                            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>Previous research shows that sleep habits strongly affect health and wellbeing. In Bhutan, the Gross National Happiness (GNH) survey found that people who sleep too little or too much report worse health outcomes. Studies also highlight that poor sleep quality is linked to low energy, depression, and reduced daily functioning, especially among older adults, nurses, and people with chronic illness.</run>
                            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>Globally, research consistently finds that long screen time especially before bedtime delays sleep, reduces sleep quality, and increases daytime sleepiness. Work-related factors, like long or irregular hours, also contribute to poor sleep and low energy.</run>
                            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>These patterns suggest that lifestyle habits sleep routines, screen use, and work schedules directly influence daily energy and overall wellbeing. However, in Bhutan, little research has compared these habits between urban and rural residents, where work types, access to technology, and daily routines differ significantly.</run>
                            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>This evidence establishes that sleep-related lifestyle issues exist and may be impacting health and energy in Bhutan, justifying the need for a comparative study of urban and rural populations.</run>
                          </formatted-text>
                        </zone>
                      </dashboard>
                    </capturedDeltas>
                  </story-point>
                  <story-point caption='Why Self-Care Matters, Local Context, and               Purpose of the Study' captured-sheet='Dashboard 7' id='19' />
                  <story-point caption='Overview' captured-sheet='' id='31' />
                  <story-point caption='Respondent Distribution' captured-sheet='Demographics (2)' id='20'>
                    <capturedDeltas>
                      <dashboard name='Demographics (2)'>
                        <zone id='41'>
                          <formatted-text />
                        </zone>
                      </dashboard>
                    </capturedDeltas>
                  </story-point>
                  <story-point caption='1. Core insights: Average Work pattern ' captured-sheet='core' id='21' />
                  <story-point caption='2. Core insights: Average Screen use pattern ' captured-sheet='core (2)' id='22' />
                  <story-point caption='3. Core insights:  Average Sleep pattern' captured-sheet='core (3)' id='23' />
                  <story-point caption='4. Correlation Insights: Average Working Hours and Sleep quality and day energy level ' captured-sheet='Behav' id='24' />
                  <story-point caption='5. Correlation Insights: Average Screenuse Hours and Sleep quality and day energy level ' captured-sheet='Behav (2)' id='25' />
                  <story-point caption='6. Correlation Insights: Average Sleep Hours and Sleep quality and day energy level ' captured-sheet='Behav (3)' id='26' />
                  <story-point caption='Habits That Influence Sleep Quality' captured-sheet='Improvement' id='11'>
                    <capturedDeltas>
