        <zone friendly-name='Average work hours' h='62857' id='3' name='Average work hours' w='31231' x='1077' y='35179' />
        <zone h='32321' id='22' name='Work types' w='97692' x='1538' y='1786' />
        <zone forceUpdate='true' h='59643' id='28' type-v2='text' w='54615' x='44154' y='41964'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>The survey data highlights differences in work types and hours between rural and urban residents. Among rural respondents, physical work (11.2%) is slightly more common than mental work (5.3%), while urban residents are primarily engaged in mental work (19.3%), with fewer involved in physical work (9.8%). When combining both physical and mental work, a larger share of urban residents (37.5%) falls into this category compared to rural residents (16.8%). </run>
            <run>Æ&#10;&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='11'>In terms of workload, urban residents work slightly longer hours on average (6.09 hours per day) than rural residents (5.64 hours per day).</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
      </zones>
      <devicelayouts>
